    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Porous rock such as sandstone or limestone that has become impregnated with natural asphalt through a geological process, so that the asphalt has more than 10% minerals.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
